I made this tart with key lime juice instead of lemon, and with both the shortbread crust and with a graham cracker crust. We liked the filling very much, and preferred the graham cracker crust to the shortbread. Didn't caramelize either one and they were still very good. Be sure to push the shortbread up to the top of the tart pan or all the filling won't fit!

